<section class="service-section" id="services">
  <div class="service-container">
    <!-- Full-width Header Section -->
    <div class="service-header">
      <h2>Robotic Precision Therapy</h2>
      <p class="intro">When physical therapy, chiropractic care, massage, and injections have failed, our RX 2600 Therapeutic Robot targets the root cause: deep myofascial restrictions and muscular imbalances that cause chronic back pain, sciatica, and structural dysfunction.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Two-Column Content Section -->
    <div class="service-content">
      <div class="features-column">
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li>Penetrates deeper than manual therapy to reach piriformis, psoas, and spinal stabilizers</li>
          <li>FDA-registered technology used in professional sports and rehabilitation centers nationwide</li>
          <li>Treats herniated discs, bulging discs, sciatica, SI joint dysfunction, and spinal stenosis</li>
          <li>Personalized protocols for chronic lower back pain, upper back pain, and radiating leg pain</li>
          <li>Proven results: 87% of patients report significant pain reduction within 6 sessions</li>
          <li>No downtime—return to work and daily activities immediately after treatment</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="image-column">
        <img src="public/therapy-machine.jpg" alt="RX 2600 Robotic Therapy Machine in Action" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .service-section {
    padding: 100px 2rem;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .service-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  /* Full-Width Header Section */
  .service-header {
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .service-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #40c557 50%, #228b22 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: #b8b8b8;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Two-Column Content Section */
  .service-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .features-column {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .features-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .features-list li {
    padding: 1rem 0;
    color: #b8b8b8;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .features-list li:hover {
    color: #40c557;
    transform: translateX(10px);
  }

  .features-list li::before {
    content: "✓";
    color: #40c557;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-right: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  .image-column {
    position: relative;
  }

  .image-column img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(64, 197, 87, 0.3);
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: zoomInFade 1.2s ease 0.3s forwards;
  }

  .image-column img:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05) translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 35px 70px rgba(64, 197, 87, 0.5);
  }

  @keyframes zoomInFade {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: scale(0.85) translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1) translateY(0);
    }
  }

  /* Tablet Layout */
  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .service-section {
      padding: 80px 2rem;
    }

    .service-container {
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .service-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .service-header h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }

    .intro {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .features-list li {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }

  /* Mobile Layout */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .service-section {
      padding: 60px 1rem;
    }

    .service-container {
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .service-header h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .intro {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .features-list li {
      padding: 0.8rem 0;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .features-list li::before {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-right: 0.8rem;
    }
  }
</style>
